OL,3,CThree more arrests after arson attack
OL,4,Con Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FThree more people have been arrested
OL,7,Fafter four Jewish community ambulances
OL,8,Fwere targeted in an alleged arson
OL,9,Fattack in north-west London.
OL,11,FTwo British men, aged 19 and 20, and a
OL,12,F17-year-old dual British-Pakistani
OL,13,Fnational, were arrested at separate
OL,14,Faddresses in east London on Wednesday.
OL,16,FThey were all held on suspicion of
OL,17,Fconspiracy to commit arson with intent
OL,18,Fto endanger life and their homes are
OL,19,Fbeing searched.
